WEBVTT

03:33.066 --> 03:35.274
-I can't do it.
-You must!

03:35.316 --> 03:38.108
There is only one piece of evidence
the police can use to prove this.

03:38.149 --> 03:39.858
-Our own fear.
-Watch closely, sir.

03:40.066 --> 03:41.733
If he's afraid deep down,

03:41.774 --> 03:43.274
he'll turn around
and look back at us.

03:47.399 --> 03:48.399
Last Saturday...

03:48.733 --> 03:51.274
I mean, August 2nd, Saturday...

03:51.649 --> 03:52.774
Where were you?

03:53.399 --> 03:55.399
We were at a spiritual
retreat in Thodupuzha.

03:57.358 --> 03:59.191
He just recreated that day.

03:59.483 --> 04:03.649
He recreated the dates...
August 2nd and 3rd.
